@startuml
title 个性化偏好与设备别名参与执行顺序图（紧凑视图）
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam SequenceParticipantFontSize 20
skinparam SequenceMessageFontSize 19
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam Shadowing false
hide footbox

actor "家庭用户" as User
participant "前端语音页" as FE
participant "后端指令接口" as API
participant "个性化服务" as Personal
participant "指令执行链路" as Chain
database "SQLite" as DB

User -> FE: 执行命令
FE -> API: POST /api/commands/execute
API -> Personal: 读取偏好、匹配设备别名
Personal -> DB: 查询偏好和别名
DB --> Personal: 个性化上下文
Personal --> Chain: 命令文本 + alias_match
Chain -> Chain: 纠错 / 归一 / 解析 / 校验
Chain -> DB: 记录日志
Chain --> API: 执行结果
API --> FE: 展示结果
@enduml
